      "file_path": "participant/participant-impl/participant-impl-simulator/src/main/resources/config/application.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 5,
      "message": "yes, and there is the issue on how to change the passwords if it affects this application, security tools will flag this on static analysis I think.   In general, I think the use of credentials and localhost references in resources files needs attention.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 477,
